      <h3>How do I know if a drain issue is a main line problem?</h3>
      <p>
        If multiple fixtures are slow or backing up at the same time, it may be a larger branch line or main line restriction rather than a single fixture clog.
      </p>

      <h3>Should I keep using chemical drain cleaners?</h3>
      <p>
        Repeated use can damage pipes and make repairs harder. A diagnostic-first clearing method is usually safer and more effective.
      </p>

      <h3>Can you repair or replace water heaters?</h3>
